{"tid":1925045,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處嘅「機靈行動」有幾機靈？","createTime":"2020-03-14T05:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T16:01:27.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb98611bc47ba98a8f30b00a4e8935adaa3b47f","tid":1925045,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反非法勞工行動拘二十八人<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n    入境事務處（入境處）一連四日（三月九至十二日）在全港各區展開代號「曙光行動」及<span style=\"color: red;\">「機靈行動」</span>的反非法勞工行動，共拘捕十七名懷疑非法勞工及十一名涉嫌聘用非法勞工的人士。<br />\n<br />\n  行動中，入境處特遣隊人員搜查了七十二個目標地點，包括停車場、公司、食品工場、生果檔、垃圾站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、工業大廈、美甲店、公園、住宅大廈、餐廳、店鋪及貨倉。被捕的懷疑非法勞工為九男八女，年齡介乎二十一至五十三歲。當中四名男子持有不允許僱傭工作的擔保書（俗稱「行街紙」）。另外，三男五女涉嫌管有及行使懷疑偽造身份證或他人身份證。此外，一名男子涉嫌管有及行使虛假文書。因涉嫌聘用非法勞工被捕的僱主則為九男兩女，年齡介乎二十九至五十三歲。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n洗唔洗叫大軍？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=2diban0/66or000510o02n6p3o89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2diban0%2F66or000510o02n6p3o89.jpg&h=787294f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXHmgkU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXHmgkU.jpg&h=55527b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191204/_2019120416520144034.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191204%2F_2019120416520144034.jpg&h=8d4c13e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"496cfc9c455a3f6c6442936c70932253ce58f175","tid":1925045,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"你以為的曙光行動：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pzjvgZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpzjvgZp.jpg&h=939f4497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入境處的曙光行動：<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190521/photo/bkn-20190521164801054-0521_00822_001_01p.jpg?2019